# ============================================================================
# run_point.mac — DEPRECATED stub, kept only so CMake's configure_file()
# rule for this path keeps working. The energy sweep no longer uses
# /control/foreach: energy_scan.mac (generated by generate_energy_scan.py)
# inlines every point, because file names need the 'p'-encoded energy tag
# (0.001 -> 0p001) while /gun/energy needs the numeric value, and a foreach
# alias cannot provide both. Safe to delete once the CMakeLists.txt entry
# for macros/run_point.mac is removed.
# ============================================================================
